e%20feature%20set%20running.%0AFirst%20we%20can%20use%20short%20youtube%20style%20urls%20for%20our%20content%20now.%20Much%20easier%20to%20share%20and%20to%20look%20at.%0AYou%20can%20save%20preferences%20associated%20to%20your%20user%20profile,%20just%20two%20options%20for%20the%20beginning,%20more%20will%20follow%20soon.%0AAnd%20finally%20there%20is%20a%20search%20interface%20to%20the%20catalog%20of%20generated%20content.%20Start%20browsing%20through%20the%20slides%20we%20have%20available%20so%20far</paragraph><paragraph encoding="UTF-8-PCT-ENCODED" role="note" id="slide-00003" xml-lang="en-NZ">Hi%20this%20is%20Frederik,%20with%20a%20quick%20update%20on%20the%20backend%20development%20process.%0AAs%20I%20started%20the%20work%20two%20weeks%20ago,%20it%20was%20quite%20a%20mission%20to%20get%20everything%20setup%20for%20development%20so%20Jasper%20and%20I%20have%20been%20working%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20things%20to%20make%20it%20as%20easy%20as%20possible%20for%20new%20developers%20to%20join%20the%20team.%0AWe%20can%20now%20distribute%20the%20whole%20application%20server%20as%20a%20virtual%20machine%20(KVM%20for%20development%20on%20Linux%20or%20VMWare%20on%20Windows)%20and%20connect%20with%20Maven%20for%20deployment%20and%20testing.%0ATo%20get%20the%20tests%20executed%20inside%20the%20actual%20running%20application%20we%20chose%20the%20arquillian%20framework.%20This%20approach%20enables%20you%20to%20test%20and%20debug%20in%20the%20real%20%20environment%20and%20makes%20testing%20across%20different%20virtual%20machines%20a%20breeze.%0AUsing%20this%20toolchain%20an%20experienced%20java%20developer%20can%20set%20up%20his%20development%20environment%20quite%20easily.%20We%20could%20make%20this%20even%20easier%20by%20copying%20a%20whole%20preconfigured%20Eclipse%20IDE%20for%20example%20if%20someone%20just%20wants%20to%20take%20on%20a%20specific%20smaller%20task%0A</paragraph><paragraph encoding="UTF-8-PCT-ENCODED" role="note" id="slide-00004" xml-lang="en-NZ">This%20is%20our%20agenda%20for%20the%20next%20weeks,%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20Jasper%20will%20be%20to%20connect%20with%20James%20work%20on%20the%20design%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20technical%20look%20of%20our%20system.%0AFred%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20conversion%20process%20first,%20to%20make%20it%20as%20robust%20as%20possible%20and%20give%20more%20detailed%20information%20to%20the%20user.%20Following%20the%20apache%20lucene%20search%20engine%20wil%20be%20integrated.%0AThen%20Jasper%20is%20going%20to%20add%20some%20more%20features%20to%20the%20web%20application%20and%20the%20endpoints%20to%20enable%20users%20to%20add%20metadata%20to%20the%20catalog%20as%20well%20and%20connect%20those%20to%20the%20Lucene%20search%20engine%0AAs%20soon%20as%20this%20is%20on%20the%20way,%20Jasper%20will%20extend%20the%20html5%20slideview%20and%20implement%20vertical%20switching%20between%20languages.%0A</paragraph></body></notedocument>